YoY Volume 13

1.     Right Click on YoY Sales  and select Duplicate . Change the name of the sheet to YOY Volume. Remove all the fields from the marks shelf.



2. Drag and drop to the Text under Marks

   <AGG(_Volume YOY % )>

   <AGG(cc. Mark Volume KPI Indicator UP)>

  <AGG(cc. Mark Volume KPI Indicator Down)>

3. Right click on YOY Volume under marks shelf and select format > Pane > Numbers Custom > Percentage > Decimal places 2



4. Click on Text select the ellipses (…) and Highlight all the text select Tableau Bold. Select Font size 12 and Font type Bold. Click on the Alignment and select Horizontal Center and Vertical Center.





5. Click on the Text and select    <AGG(_Volume YOY % )> and change the color to blue

( #4e79a7) Likewise select <AGG(cc. Mark Volume KPI Indicator UP)> and change the color to Green (  #59a14f ) . select   <AGG(cc. Mark Volume KPI Indicator Down)> and change the color to Red (#e15759). Arrange in one line Click Ok.







6.Rt Click on the tile and select Edit title  and select the title YoY Volume Tableau Semi bold> font size 10 > font type bold > Color Black >Alignment as Center
